- \b Pattern recognition:\b0  High. He recognized that Cursor could be used not just for code generation but for communications transformation.\par
- \b Systems thinking:\b0  High. He connected deliverables, stakeholder messaging, formats, advocacy goals, and presentation strategy.\par
- \b Strategic judgment:\b0  High. He showed awareness that producing the artifact is only half the job; positioning it for leadership acceptance is equally important.\par
- \b Verbal intelligence:\b0  High. His asks consistently center around tone, framing, audience, and positioning.\par
- \b Creative synthesis:\b0  Very high. He appears able to combine storytelling, design intent, advocacy messaging, and technical tooling into a coherent whole.\par
