If an honest shorthand is needed, Jordan does \b not\b0  read like an average first-time AI user. He reads like an unusually capable novice whose ceiling may be far above his current formal technical training. In plain language: he may still be new to coding, but he does not appear ordinary in the way he learns, applies, and expands these tools.\par
